*term-list*/
.term-list{
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: 37px;
}
.term-list__single{
    margin-bottom: 26px;
}
.term-list dt{
    line-height: 1.56;
}
.term-list dt,
.term-list dd{
    position: relative;
}

.term-list dt:before{
    position: absolute;
    width: 27px;
    height: 27px;
    text-align: center;
    right: 100%;
    margin-right: 13px;
    top: 3px;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: 21px;
}
.term-list dd{
    padding-left: 20px;
}
.term-list dd:before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    -webkit-transform: translateY(-50%);
    -moz-transform: translateY(-50%);
    -ms-transform: translateY(-50%);
    -o-transform: translateY(-50%);
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 3px;
    height: 3px;
    -webkit-border-radius: 999px;
    -moz-border-radius: 999px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background-color: #212121;
}
.term-list dt.icon-bike:before {
    font-size: 14px;
}
.term-list dd + dt{
    margin-top: 13px;
}
